00:02.321 --> 00:03.700
You seem to know Bowie.

00:03.958 --> 00:04.959
You could say that.

00:04.991 --> 00:06.927
Do you know if he's seeing anyone?

00:06.959 --> 00:09.501
- I don't think so...
- 'Cause I was thinking I'd like to...

00:09.526 --> 00:10.607
<i>ask him out.</i>

00:10.632 --> 00:12.211
BOWIE: <i> So Morgan did
steal the prayer box.</i>

00:12.235 --> 00:13.604
<i>And you knew she stole it?</i>

00:13.877 --> 00:15.677
You made it look like
it was all Andi's fault.

00:15.701 --> 00:16.837
BEX: <i> So, um,</i>

00:16.870 --> 00:17.905
you and Miranda?

