00:26.833 --> 00:28.035
like... you.

00:29.973 --> 00:31.208
Okay, everybody!

00:31.242 --> 00:33.376
Write down a wish you want
to send up in your lantern.

00:33.409 --> 00:34.849
(ALL CHEERING)

00:36.212 --> 00:37.326
♪ ♪

00:41.629 --> 00:42.629
Whoa...

00:43.653 --> 00:44.909
♪♪

00:49.894 --> 00:51.394
<i>♪ I walk in like how do you do ♪</i>

00:51.428 --> 00:53.631
<i>♪ And I don't mean to be
rude, or even act a fool ♪</i>

00:53.663 --> 00:56.233
<i>♪ I just do a little better
with an attitude ♪</i>

00:56.266 --> 00:58.435
<i>♪ So riki tiki tiki tum tum ♪</i>

00:58.468 --> 01:00.103
<i>♪ Sticky icky icky
like it's Bubble Yum ♪</i>

01:00.137 --> 01:01.572
<i>♪ Getting some, going dumb ♪</i>

01:01.605 --> 01:02.949
<i>♪ Maybe we shut it down
when trouble gets loud ♪</i>

01:02.973 --> 01:05.409
<i>♪ It's on the tip of your tongue ♪</i>

01:05.441 --> 01:07.110
♪ Turn the bass up ♪

01:07.143 --> 01:10.080
<i>♪ Girl pick your face up ♪</i>

01:10.113 --> 01:12.983
<i>♪ I wanna see you move ♪</i>

01:14.784 --> 01:15.792
<i>♪ Turn the lights down ♪</i>

01:15.817 --> 01:16.894
CYRUS: Hey!

01:16.919 --> 01:18.155
<i>♪ It's gonna get loud ♪</i>

01:18.188 --> 01:19.156
(MUSIC STOPS)

01:19.190 --> 01:20.925
It's looking good!

01:21.184 --> 01:22.185
You like it?

01:22.217 --> 01:23.491
- BUFFY: We love it!
- CYRUS: Like it?

01:23.515 --> 01:25.371
I can't believe you made
it look like a barn.

01:25.494 --> 01:27.310
It's got everything but a weather-vane.

01:28.724 --> 01:29.735
- (CYRUS EXHALES)
- (CHUCKLES)

01:29.759 --> 01:31.135
Anything we can do to help?

01:31.160 --> 01:32.710
Oh, no, no, no, no, no.

01:32.735 --> 01:34.010
It's basically done.

01:35.663 --> 01:36.597
(MUSIC STARTS AGAIN)

01:36.622 --> 01:38.232
<i>♪ All day looking like you're 'Yonce ♪</i>

01:38.257 --> 01:39.527
<i>♪ Sippin on some... ♪</i>

01:39.560 --> 01:41.328
I love group projects.

01:41.361 --> 01:42.696
So fun.

01:42.729 --> 01:43.829
