01:53.972 --> 01:56.842
<i>♪ Life is upside down ♪</i>

01:57.147 --> 02:02.052
<i>♪ But any way it goes I'll work it out ♪</i>

02:03.347 --> 02:06.752
<i>♪ Oh oh oh oh oh ♪</i>

