23:01.497 --> 23:02.819
ANDI: <i> Next, on</i> Andi Mack.

23:02.844 --> 23:04.645
Metcalf just announced costume day.

23:04.670 --> 23:05.910
That's too soon!

23:05.935 --> 23:08.638
Guys, hello! We know
what we're gonna be!

23:08.663 --> 23:10.335
Mount Rushmore!

23:10.905 --> 23:12.774
What you got goin' on for costume day?

23:12.808 --> 23:14.127
Costume day?

23:14.152 --> 23:15.921
You don't strike me
as a costume day guy.

23:16.345 --> 23:17.522
Do you think Andi'll still be my friend

23:17.546 --> 23:19.083
if I bail on Mount Rushmore?

23:19.108 --> 23:20.509
Quick answer, no.

23:21.082 --> 23:23.819
- I need a sheet!
- BEX: Huh?

23:23.853 --> 23:26.055
For a costume!

23:26.088 --> 23:27.088
Wait, let me help you!

